62
00:06:27,153 --> 00:06:28,780
POINTS TO AN EVENT

63
00:06:28,855 --> 00:06:31,722
KNOWN AS ''THE MASSACRE
OF THE INNOCENTS''

64
00:06:31,791 --> 00:06:34,089
WHICH OCCURRED
IN FIRST CENTURY JUDEA.

65
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:36,720
IN THE DECADES LEADING UP
TO THE BIRTH OF CHRIST,

66
00:06:36,796 --> 00:06:38,093
THE ROMAN EMPIRE

67
00:06:38,164 --> 00:06:39,995
HAD CONQUERED THE WHOLE
MEDITERRANEAN WORLD,

68
00:06:40,066 --> 00:06:41,795
INCLUDING JUDEA.

69
00:06:41,868 --> 00:06:43,927
AND AT VARIOUS POINTS
IN THAT HISTORY

70
00:06:44,003 --> 00:06:46,733
THEY HAD DIFFERENT PEOPLE
RULING OVER IT.

71
00:06:46,806 --> 00:06:50,401
TWENTY YEARS BEFORE JESUS
WAS BORN YOU HAVE KING HEROD,

72
00:06:50,476 --> 00:06:53,343
A CLIENT KING FOR ROME.

73
00:06:53,413 --> 00:06:56,041
WE HAVE DOCUMENTS
ABOUT HIM OUTSIDE THE BIBLE

74
00:06:56,115 --> 00:06:58,413
THAT TELL US
THAT HE WAS VERY CRUEL.

75
00:06:58,484 --> 00:07:00,918
HE WAS CAPABLE
OF KILLING HIS OWN SONS.

76
00:07:00,987 --> 00:07:02,284
HE WAS RUTHLESS

77
00:07:02,355 --> 00:07:05,813
AND YOU WOULDN'T WANT
TO GET ON HIS BAD SIDE.

78
00:07:05,892 --> 00:07:07,757
HEROD WAS VERY ANXIOUS

79
00:07:07,827 --> 00:07:10,694
WHEN A SMALL DELEGATION
OF WISE MEN FROM THE EAST

80
00:07:10,763 --> 00:07:12,253
CAME TO JERUSALEM

81
00:07:12,331 --> 00:07:15,994
ANNOUNCING THEIR SEARCH
FOR THE NEWBORN KING OF THE JEWS.

82
00:07:16,068 --> 00:07:17,797
WHY WOULD HEROD
BE UPSET ABOUT THAT?

83
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:21,033
BECAUSE THAT WAS HEROD'S TITLE
AS BESTOWED UPON HIM

84
00:07:21,107 --> 00:07:23,837
BY THE ROMAN EMPIRE:
KING OF THE JEWS.

85
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:26,208
AND HE ASKS
HIS ASTROLOGERS,

86
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,769
''HOW LONG IS IT POSSIBLE

87
00:07:27,847 --> 00:07:29,712
THIS CHILD
COULD HAVE BEEN BORN AGO?''

88
00:07:29,782 --> 00:07:31,044
AND THEY DETERMINE

89
00:07:31,117 --> 00:07:33,017
IT'S PROBABLY BEEN
MAYBE 2 YEARS AT MOST

90
00:07:33,085 --> 00:07:35,144
SINCE THIS CHILD WAS BORN,
MAYBE LESS.

91
00:07:35,221 --> 00:07:40,386
HE FINDS OUT FROM
THE PHARISEES AND THE SADDUCEES

92
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:43,486
EXACTLY WHERE THIS CHILD
WAS TO BE BORN

93
00:07:43,763 --> 00:07:45,355
AND HE FINDS OUT
IT'S BETHLEHEM

94
00:07:45,431 --> 00:07:48,195
AND HE WORRIED
ABOUT LOSING HIS THRONE.

95
00:07:48,267 --> 00:07:50,963
AND SO HE HAS SUCH ANGER
AGAINST THIS CHILD

96
00:07:51,037 --> 00:07:55,906
HE SENDS IN THE SOLDIERS
TO TRY AND KILL JESUS.

97
00:09:05,111 --> 00:09:08,171
THE BIBLE TELLS US
THIS BARBARIC ACT

98
00:09:08,247 --> 00:09:11,307
WAS INSPIRED BY MORE THAN JUST
THE TYRANNICAL JEALOUSY

99
00:09:11,384 --> 00:09:13,011
OF AN OLD KING.

100
00:09:13,085 --> 00:09:14,985
MANY BIBLE SCHOLARS BELIEVE

101
00:09:15,054 --> 00:09:17,215
THAT IT'S PART
OF A MUCH BIGGER STRUGGLE

102
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:21,283
THAT HAS SPANNED THE AGES
AND IS STILL HAPPENING TODAY.

103
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:24,090
TO UNCOVER THE SECRETS
OF THIS PROPHEC Y

104
00:09:24,163 --> 00:09:27,564
WE'RE GOING TO FIRST NEED
TO IDENTIFY THE MAIN CHARACTERS:

105
00:09:27,633 --> 00:09:31,592
THE WOMAN, THE CHILD
AND THE DRAGON.

106
00:09:31,871 --> 00:09:35,329
HE SAYS, ''THEN I SAW
ANOTHER SIGN, A WOMAN,

107
00:09:35,408 --> 00:09:38,536
''CLOTHED WITH THE SUN,
WITH THE MOON UNDER HER FEET,

108
00:09:38,611 --> 00:09:42,069
AND ON HER HEAD A CROWN
OF TWELVE STARS.''

109
00:09:42,148 --> 00:09:44,844
LET'S TAKE A CLOSER LOOK
AT THE WOMAN.

110
00:09:44,917 --> 00:09:49,217
WE KNOW THAT SHE'S A SYMBOL
OF SOMEONE OR SOMETHING.

111
00:09:50,289 --> 00:09:54,385
DOES THE BIBLE TELL US
WHAT THIS WOMAN REPRESENTS?

112
00:09:56,929 --> 00:09:58,556
''HUSBANDS LOVE YOUR WIVES,

113
00:09:58,631 --> 00:10:00,622
''JUST AS CHRIST
LOVED THE CHURCH

114
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:04,267
AND GAVE HIMSELF FOR HER.''

115
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:06,165
WE GATHER FROM THIS

116
00:10:06,238 --> 00:10:08,399
THAT THE CHURCH
IS THE BRIDE OF CHRIST.

117
00:10:08,474 --> 00:10:10,465
NOT ONLY
IS SHE THE BRIDE OF CHRIST

118
00:10:10,543 --> 00:10:14,377
BUT IN A CERTAIN SENSE,
SINCE NO MAN HATES HIS OWN FLESH,

119
00:10:14,447 --> 00:10:17,280
THE CHURCH IS JESUS' BODY.

120
00:10:17,350 --> 00:10:19,409
VERY CLEARLY A WOMAN,
IN SCRIPTURE,

121
00:10:19,485 --> 00:10:21,385
REPRESENTS THE CHURCH.

122
00:10:21,454 --> 00:10:25,288
YOU HAVE A WOMAN
AS REPRESENTATIVE OF GOD'S PEOPLE.

123
00:10:25,358 --> 00:10:26,620
WE SEE THIS
IN THE OLD TESTAMENT.

124
00:10:26,692 --> 00:10:28,489
WE SEE IT IN THE NEW TESTAMENT.

125
00:10:28,561 --> 00:10:30,392
JESUS COMES
FROM THE PEOPLE OF ISRAEL

126
00:10:30,463 --> 00:10:33,091
AND THEN THE CHURCH GROWS UP

127
00:10:33,165 --> 00:10:35,963
AS SOMETHING
THAT JESUS DEVELOPS.

128
00:10:36,035 --> 00:10:39,527
MOST IMPORTANTLY, THIS WOMAN
IS ABOUT TO GIVE BIRTH

129
00:10:39,605 --> 00:10:42,267
TO A SPECIAL MALE CHILD.

130
00:10:42,341 --> 00:10:43,968
WHO IS THE CHILD?

131
00:10:44,043 --> 00:10:45,374
WE HAVE
A COUPLE OF INDICATIONS:

132
00:10:45,444 --> 00:10:49,005
ONE: HE RULES WITH A ROD OF IRON
OVER THE NATIONS.

133
00:10:49,081 --> 00:10:51,641
THAT'S A REFERENCE
TO THE OLD TESTAMENT

134
00:10:51,717 --> 00:10:53,514
WHERE CLEARLY
GOD IS THE ONE

135
00:10:53,586 --> 00:10:56,680
RULING OVER THE NATIONS
WITH A ROD OF IRON.

136
00:10:56,956 --> 00:10:59,424
AND THEN HE SAYS
HE'S CAUGHT UP INTO HEAVEN

137
00:10:59,492 --> 00:11:01,289
AND WHO IS CAUGHT UP
INTO HEAVEN?

138
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,691
JESUS CHRIST, RIGHT?

139
00:11:02,962 --> 00:11:05,021
HE'S THE KING OF KINGS
AND LORD OF LORDS.

140
00:11:05,097 --> 00:11:07,156
SO THESE TWO INDICATIONS
PRETTY DEFINITIVELY TELL US

141
00:11:07,233 --> 00:11:09,064
THAT THIS IS JESUS.

142
00:11:09,135 --> 00:11:11,626
NOW LET'S CONSIDER
THE ARCH VILLAIN

143
00:11:11,704 --> 00:11:15,162
IN THIS IMPORTANT PROPHEC Y:
THE DRAGON.

144
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:18,568
''AND ANOTHER SIGN
APPEARED IN HEAVEN:

145
00:11:18,644 --> 00:11:22,171
BEHOLD, A GREAT,
FIERY RED DRAGON...''

146
00:11:24,216 --> 00:11:27,413
I WISH I COULD JUST GIVE YOU
A FANCIFUL THEORY HERE,

147
00:11:27,486 --> 00:11:29,954
BUT THE BIBLE TELLS US
WHO THE DRAGON IS.

148
00:11:30,022 --> 00:11:32,388
THE DRAGON IS THE DEVIL.

149
00:11:32,458 --> 00:11:34,551
BOTH IN THE OLD TESTAMENT
AND THE NEW TESTAMENT

150
00:11:34,627 --> 00:11:36,094
WHO TRIES TO DESTROY?

151
00:11:36,162 --> 00:11:38,027
THAT IS SATAN,
THE ANGEL, THE DEVIL.

152
00:11:38,097 --> 00:11:39,359
AND SO HE ATTACKS

153
00:11:39,432 --> 00:11:42,424
AS SOON AS CHRIST COMES
UPON THE FACE OF THE EARTH;

154
00:11:42,501 --> 00:11:44,366
THE ATTACK IS THERE.

155
00:11:45,705 --> 00:11:48,265
''SO THE GREAT DRAGON
WAS CAST OUT,

156
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:51,639
''THAT SERPENT OF OLD,
CALLED THE DEVIL AND SATAN.

157
00:11:51,711 --> 00:11:53,679
''WHO DECEIVES
THE WHOLE WORLD;

158
00:11:53,746 --> 00:11:55,475
''HE WAS CAST TO THE EARTH,

159
00:11:55,548 --> 00:11:58,415
AND HIS ANGELS
WERE CAST OUT WITH HIM.''

160
00:12:00,319 --> 00:12:03,755
WHAT WE SEE HERE
IN THE FIRST PART OF REVELATION 1 2

161
00:12:04,023 --> 00:12:05,650
IS A SYMBOLIC PORTRAYAL

162
00:12:05,725 --> 00:12:09,684
OF THE AGE-OLD CONFLICT
BETWEEN CHRIST AND SATAN.

163
00:12:09,762 --> 00:12:11,491
AND WE FIND THIS DESCRIPTION

164
00:12:11,564 --> 00:12:14,260
GOING ALL THE WAY BACK
TO THE GARDEN OF EDEN

165
00:12:14,333 --> 00:12:16,096
WHERE YOU HAVE
A SNAKE WITH WINGS.

166
00:12:16,168 --> 00:12:19,137
WHAT'S A SNAKE WITH WINGS?
IT'S A FORM OF A DRAGON.

167
00:12:19,205 --> 00:12:21,070
AND WE HAVE THIS SERPENT,
THIS DRAGON,

168
00:12:21,140 --> 00:12:23,472
COMING ALL THE WAY DOWN
THROUGH SCRIPTURES.

169
00:12:23,542 --> 00:12:26,033
ALL THROUGH THE LIFE
AND MINISTRY OF CHRIST

170
00:12:26,112 --> 00:12:28,637
SATAN TRIED TO DISRUPT
JESUS' PLANS

171
00:12:28,714 --> 00:12:31,615
TO PROVIDE SALVATION
FOR HUMANITY.

172
00:12:33,185 --> 00:12:35,676
''BUT HE WAS WOUNDED
FOR OUR TRANSGRESSIONS,

173
00:12:35,755 --> 00:12:38,121
''HE WAS BRUISED
FOR OUR INIQUITIES;

174
00:12:38,190 --> 00:12:41,353
''THE CHASTISEMENT
FOR OUR PEACE WAS UPON HIM,

175
00:12:41,427 --> 00:12:44,123
AND BY HIS STRIPES
WE ARE HEALED.''

176
00:12:46,599 --> 00:12:48,794
AT VARIOUS POINTS
THEY KICKED HIM OUT OF SYNAGOGUES

177
00:12:49,068 --> 00:12:50,797
AND WANTED
TO PUSH HIM OFF A CLIFF.

178
00:12:51,070 --> 00:12:52,401
THEY TRIED TO SILENCE HIM.

179
00:12:52,471 --> 00:12:55,065
THEY TORTURED HIM
TO DEATH PUBLICLY.

180
00:12:55,141 --> 00:12:58,372
BUT SATAN'S SCHEME
TO DERAIL THE PLAN OF SALVATION

181
00:12:58,444 --> 00:13:02,437
WAS UTTERLY SHATTERED
WHEN JESUS ROSE FROM THE DEAD.

182
00:13:05,484 --> 00:13:09,250
''AND HER CHILD WAS CAUGHT UP
TO GOD AND HIS THRONE.''

183
00:13:10,589 --> 00:13:13,786
WITH THE SON OF GOD
NOW PHYSICALLY BEYOND HIS REACH,

184
00:13:13,859 --> 00:13:17,659
THE DEVIL DIRECTED ALL OF HIS FURY
AT THE FOLLOWERS OF JESUS,

185
00:13:17,730 --> 00:13:19,721
THE NEW CHRISTIANS.

186
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:21,357
HE DID MUCH OF THIS

187
00:13:21,433 --> 00:13:24,368
THROUGH THE CRUEL POWER
OF IMPERIAL ROME.

188
00:13:25,604 --> 00:13:27,128
''NOW WHEN THE DRAGON SAW

189
00:13:27,206 --> 00:13:29,140
''THAT HE HAD BEEN CAST
TO THE EARTH,

190
00:13:29,208 --> 00:13:30,505
''HE PERSECUTED THE WOMAN

191
00:13:30,576 --> 00:13:33,272
WHO GAVE BIRTH
TO THE MALE CHILD.''

192
00:13:33,345 --> 00:13:37,714
CHRISTIANITY WAS A STRUGGLING,
SMALL PERSECUTED MINORITY

193
00:13:37,783 --> 00:13:40,650
THAT DIDN'T HAVE OFFICIAL STATUS
IN THE ROMAN EMPIRE

194
00:13:40,719 --> 00:13:42,846
AND THERE WERE
A SERIES OF PERSECUTIONS,

195
00:13:43,122 --> 00:13:45,317
SOME OF WHICH
WERE QUITE SEVERE.

196
00:13:45,391 --> 00:13:48,087
ONE OF THE ROLES OF RELIGION
IN THE ROMAN EMPIRE

197
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:50,253
WAS TO ENSURE
THE WELL-BEING OF THE STATE.

198
00:13:50,329 --> 00:13:52,763
THE IDEA WAS IF THE GODS
WERE WORSHIPED PROPERLY

199
00:13:52,832 --> 00:13:54,595
THEN THEY
WOULD FAVOR THE EMPIRE

200
00:13:54,667 --> 00:13:56,259
AND IF THEY
WERE WORSHIPED IMPROPERLY

201
00:13:56,335 --> 00:13:59,327
THEN BAD THINGS
WOULD HAPPEN TO THE EMPIRE

202
00:13:59,405 --> 00:14:01,202
AS A RESULT OF DIVINE WRATH.

203
00:14:01,273 --> 00:14:06,438
THEY DO NOT WANT
TO SACRIFICE TO THE GODS

204
00:14:06,512 --> 00:14:08,776
AND THE GODS AT THAT POINT
INCLUDE THE EMPEROR.

205
00:14:08,848 --> 00:14:11,510
SO IT'S EASY
TO CONSIDER THESE PEOPLE

206
00:14:11,584 --> 00:14:13,108
RELIGIOUS SCAPEGOATS.

207
00:14:13,185 --> 00:14:14,743
BASICALLY,
IF SOMETHING'S GOING WRONG

208
00:14:14,820 --> 00:14:16,788
PROBABLY IT'S BECAUSE
THERE ARE CHRISTIANS AROUND

209
00:14:16,856 --> 00:14:19,450
WHO ARE REFUSING TO GIVE THE GODS
THEIR PROPER DUE.

210
00:14:19,525 --> 00:14:21,254
OF COURSE
YOU HAVE TO PUNISH THEM

211
00:14:21,327 --> 00:14:24,194
AND PUNISHMENT MEANT,
MOST OF THE TIME, DEATH.

212
00:14:24,263 --> 00:14:25,560
WHAT PEOPLE THOUGHT

213
00:14:25,631 --> 00:14:29,795
WAS THAT CHRISTIANS
GATHERED TOGETHER

214
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:33,703
ALSO SEEMED TO MAKE LOVE
WITH THEIR BROTHERS AND SISTERS.

215
00:14:33,772 --> 00:14:35,330
BECAUSE THERE
WERE RUMORS ABOUT THEM

216
00:14:35,407 --> 00:14:38,171
THAT THEY COMMIT INCEST.

217
00:14:38,244 --> 00:14:40,735
THE CHRISTIANS USED TO CALL
THEMSELVES ''BROTHER'' AND ''SISTER''

218
00:14:40,813 --> 00:14:43,247
AND THEY USED TO EAT
THE FLESH OF CHRIST.

219
00:14:43,315 --> 00:14:46,307
PEOPLE HEARD, APPARENTLY,

220
00:14:46,385 --> 00:14:49,149
