THE COMMUNION SERVICE

645
00:34:47,718 --> 00:34:51,449
THEY ALL DRANK FROM IT.

646
00:34:51,522 --> 00:34:51,722
ABOUT 300 YEARS AFTER CHRIST
THE CHURCH BEGAN TO DEVIATE

647
00:34:51,722 --> 00:34:55,658
ABOUT 300 YEARS AFTER CHRIST
THE CHURCH BEGAN TO DEVIATE

648
00:34:55,726 --> 00:34:57,956
FROM ANOTHER
OF THE TEN COMMANDMENTS;

649
00:34:58,029 --> 00:35:00,497
SPECIFICALLY
THE FOURTH COMMANDMENT

650
00:35:00,565 --> 00:35:01,827
THAT REQUIRES BELIEVERS

651
00:35:01,899 --> 00:35:05,801
TO REMEMBER THE <i>7</i>TH DAY
AS THE SABBATH.

652
00:35:06,671 --> 00:35:09,868
''REMEMBER THE SABBATH DAY,
TO KEEP IT HOLY.

653
00:35:09,941 --> 00:35:12,933
''SIX DAYS YOU SHALL LABOR
AND DO ALL YOUR WORK

654
00:35:13,010 --> 00:35:14,534
''BUT THE SEVENTH DAY

655
00:35:14,612 --> 00:35:17,445
IS THE SABBATH
OF THE LORD YOUR GOD.''

656
00:35:17,849 --> 00:35:20,841
IN THE ROMAN EMPIRE
JEWS ARE AN OLD RELIGION

657
00:35:20,918 --> 00:35:23,079
AND OLD RELIGIONS
ARE RESPECTED.

658
00:35:23,154 --> 00:35:25,588
WHEN THE JEWS
KEPT FIGHTING AGAINST ROME

659
00:35:25,656 --> 00:35:30,684
WHAT HAD BEEN AN UMBRELLA
OF SAFETY UNDER JUDAISM

660
00:35:30,761 --> 00:35:33,821
BECOMES A LIGHTNING ROD
TO CHRISTIANITY

661
00:35:33,898 --> 00:35:37,061
THE CHRISTIANS
BECOME ALIENATED FROM THE JEWS

662
00:35:37,135 --> 00:35:38,762
JEWS PERSECUTED THEM

663
00:35:38,836 --> 00:35:42,101
AND SO THEY TRIED TO DISTANCE
THEMSELVES FROM THE JEWS.

664
00:35:42,173 --> 00:35:43,834
CHURCH LEADERS
BEGAN TO DEVALUE

665
00:35:43,908 --> 00:35:46,843
THE SEVENTH-DAY SABBATH
OF THE TEN COMMANDMENTS

666
00:35:46,911 --> 00:35:50,540
IN PREFERENCE FOR THE MORE
POPULAR ROMAN SUNDAY.

667
00:35:50,615 --> 00:35:52,173
SOME CHRISTIANS
MISTAKENLY THOUGHT

668
00:35:52,450 --> 00:35:55,419
THAT YOU SHOULD FAST
ON THE SABBATH

669
00:35:55,486 --> 00:35:56,953
BUT YOU COULD FEAST ON SUNDAY.

670
00:35:57,021 --> 00:35:58,613
THAT'S WHAT THE PAGANS DID,

671
00:35:58,689 --> 00:36:01,123
THEY FEASTED ON SUNDAY,
FASTED ON SATURDAY.

672
00:36:01,192 --> 00:36:03,023
NOT A JEWISH CONCEPT,

673
00:36:03,094 --> 00:36:06,063
THE JEWS FASTED FRIDAY
AND FEASTED SABBATH,

674
00:36:06,130 --> 00:36:08,189
BUT THAT'S HOW
SOME CHRISTIANS THOUGHT OF IT.

675
00:36:08,466 --> 00:36:11,731
SO IF YOU'RE FASTING ON ONE DAY
AND YOU'RE FEASTING ON THE NEXT,

676
00:36:11,802 --> 00:36:14,635
YOU CAN GUESS WHICH DAY
BECOMES THE MORE POPULAR DAY.

677
00:36:14,705 --> 00:36:16,935
AND CHRIST
IS RESURRECTED ON A SUNDAY

678
00:36:17,008 --> 00:36:18,669
THERE'S A VERY NATURAL
TENDENC Y, THEREFORE,

679
00:36:18,743 --> 00:36:20,711
TO MARK THAT
AND CELEBRATE THAT.

680
00:36:20,778 --> 00:36:22,040
THERE'S A THIRD REASON

681
00:36:22,113 --> 00:36:24,604
AND THAT IS
THE INFLUENCE OF SUN WORSHIP

682
00:36:24,682 --> 00:36:26,479
THAT CREEPS INTO THE CHURCH

683
00:36:26,551 --> 00:36:29,486
AND WHEN SUN WORSHIP BEGINS
TO CREEP INTO THE CHURCH,

684
00:36:29,554 --> 00:36:31,852
CONSTANTINE
CAN MAKE USE OF THAT

685
00:36:31,923 --> 00:36:34,721
TO LEAD
TO THE EXALTATION OF SUNDAY,

686
00:36:34,792 --> 00:36:36,054
THE DAY OF THE SUN,

687
00:36:36,127 --> 00:36:39,153
AS BEING THE DAY
THAT PEOPLE SHOULD WORSHIP ON.

688
00:36:39,230 --> 00:36:40,754
THIS GRADUAL DEPARTURE

689
00:36:40,831 --> 00:36:42,799
FROM GOD'S LAW
OVER THE CENTURIES

690
00:36:42,867 --> 00:36:44,994
HAS BECOME SO WIDELY ACCEPTED

691
00:36:45,069 --> 00:36:48,095
THAT MOST ARE SHOCKED
TO LEARN THAT SUNDAY KEEPING

692
00:36:48,172 --> 00:36:50,970
HAS NO FOUNDATION
IN THE BIBLE.

693
00:36:51,042 --> 00:36:55,741
IN AD 313 CONSTANTINE
PUBLISHED THE EDICT OF MILAN,

694
00:36:55,813 --> 00:36:58,611
ESTABLISHING SUNDAY
AS A DAY OF REST.

695
00:36:58,683 --> 00:36:59,980
THE EMPEROR'S SUNDAY LAW

696
00:37:00,051 --> 00:37:02,178
HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH CHRISTIANITY,

697
00:37:02,253 --> 00:37:05,814
IT WAS ACTUALLY TO HONOR
THE MAIN GRECO-ROMAN SUN GOD

698
00:37:05,890 --> 00:37:08,256
CALLED HELIOS, OR APOLLO.

699
00:37:08,526 --> 00:37:11,552
THE EMPEROR CONSTANTINE
BECAME A CONVERT TO CHRISTIANITY

700
00:37:11,629 --> 00:37:16,623
AND ALSO, BECAUSE HE REMAINED
PARTIAL TO THE SUN GOD,

701
00:37:16,701 --> 00:37:17,963
THE EMPEROR CONSTANTINE

702
00:37:18,035 --> 00:37:21,971
MOVED THE DAY OF WORSHIP
FROM SATURDAY THE SABBATH,

703
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:26,567
AS HAD BEEN TRADITIONAL
IN JUDAISM, OBVIOUSLY,

704
00:37:26,644 --> 00:37:29,135
TO SUNDAY,
THE DAY OF THE SUN GOD.

705
00:37:29,213 --> 00:37:33,877
AND EVER SINCE CHRISTIAN FOLKS,
AT LEAST FOR THE MOST PART,

706
00:37:33,951 --> 00:37:36,920
OVERWHELMINGLY HAVE HELD
THEIR DAY OF WORSHIP ON SUNDAY

707
00:37:36,988 --> 00:37:38,819
RATHER THAN SATURDAY.

708
00:37:38,889 --> 00:37:41,756
THIS IS CLEAR FROM ANOTHER
EDICT OF CONSTANTINE,

709
00:37:41,826 --> 00:37:45,660
GIVEN IN AD 321 ,
WHEN THE EMPEROR ORDERED:

710
00:37:45,730 --> 00:37:47,891
''ON THE VENERABLE
DAY OF THE SUN

711
00:37:47,965 --> 00:37:51,833
''LET THE MAGISTRATES AND PEOPLE
RESIDING IN CITIES REST,

712
00:37:51,902 --> 00:37:54,530
AND LET ALL WORKSHOPS
BE CLOSED.''

713
00:37:54,605 --> 00:37:59,133
NOTICE, THE EDICT
USES THE WORD ''SUN,'' S-U-N.

714
00:37:59,210 --> 00:38:01,770
IT'S ALSO RECORDED
THAT CONSTANTINE THE GREAT

715
00:38:01,846 --> 00:38:04,246
MADE A LAW
FOR THE WHOLE EMPIRE

716
00:38:04,315 --> 00:38:08,684
THAT SUNDAY SHOULD BE KEPT
AS A DAY OF REST.

717
00:38:08,753 --> 00:38:13,747
OBVIOUSLY, THIS CHANGE DID NOT
INFILTRATE THE CHURCH OVERNIGHT.

718
00:38:13,824 --> 00:38:17,726
HISTORY TELLS US THAT FOR DECADES
THE SEVENTH-DAY SABBATH,

719
00:38:17,795 --> 00:38:21,925
TOGETHER WITH SUNDAY,
WERE BOTH OBSERVED AS HOLY DAYS.

720
00:38:21,999 --> 00:38:23,796
THE VERY, VERY EARLY CHURCH

721
00:38:23,868 --> 00:38:26,063
CLEARLY IS STILL WORSHIPING
ON THE JEWISH SATURDAY

722
00:38:26,137 --> 00:38:27,934
IN THE TIMES
OF THE APOSTLES,

723
00:38:28,005 --> 00:38:31,771
BUT BY THE MID
TO LATE 3RD CENTURY,

724
00:38:31,842 --> 00:38:34,106
THAT HAS LARGELY
BEEN ABANDONED

725
00:38:34,178 --> 00:38:36,237
OR IS IN THE PROCESS
OF BEING ABANDONED.

726
00:38:36,314 --> 00:38:41,149
BY THE EARLY FOURTH CENTURY,
IN MANY PARTS OF THE ROMAN WORLD,

727
00:38:41,218 --> 00:38:43,243
CHRISTIANS ARE GENERALLY
WORSHIPING ON SUNDAY.

728
00:38:43,321 --> 00:38:45,915
A LOT OF CHRISTIANS,
DURING THIS PERIOD OF TIME,

729
00:38:45,990 --> 00:38:47,753
WOULD OBSERVE THE SABBATH

730
00:38:47,825 --> 00:38:51,261
AND THEN ON SUNDAY
THEY WOULD HAVE A SERVICE

731
00:38:51,329 --> 00:38:52,887
REMEMBERING THE RESURRECTION

732
00:38:52,963 --> 00:38:55,363
AND THEN THEY'D GO
ABOUT THEIR REGULAR WORK.

733
00:38:55,633 --> 00:38:57,931
IT'S DURING
THE TIME OF CONSTANTINE

734
00:38:58,002 --> 00:39:02,962
IN WHICH THE IDEA OF TRANSFERRING
THE SOLEMNITY OF THE SABBATH

735
00:39:03,040 --> 00:39:06,168
TO SUNDAY IS FIRST EXPRESSED.

736
00:39:06,243 --> 00:39:08,006
CENTURIES EARLIER
THE PROPHET DANIEL

737
00:39:08,079 --> 00:39:11,708
HAD FORETOLD
A RELIGIOUS POWER WOULD ARISE

738
00:39:11,782 --> 00:39:15,775
THAT WOULD THINK
TO CHANGE TIMES AND LAWS.

739
00:39:15,853 --> 00:39:18,947
WITHIN THE TEN COMMANDMENTS
THERE'S ONLY ONE LAW

740
00:39:19,023 --> 00:39:22,618
THAT IS ALSO A TIME: THE SABBATH.

741
00:39:23,928 --> 00:39:25,259
THE DOCTRINE OF HELLFIRE

742
00:39:25,329 --> 00:39:28,696
WAS ALSO DISTORTED
BY PAGAN MYTHOLOGY.

743
00:39:28,766 --> 00:39:30,256
IN THE BOOK OF REVELATION

744
00:39:30,334 --> 00:39:33,895
THE BIBLE TEACHES THAT FOLLOWING
THE GREAT JUDGMENT DAY

745
00:39:33,971 --> 00:39:36,769
THE LOST WILL BE CAST
INTO A LAKE OF FIRE.

746
00:39:36,841 --> 00:39:39,241
AT THAT TIME,
EACH PERSON IS PUNISHED

747
00:39:39,310 --> 00:39:41,335
ACCORDING TO WHAT THEY DESERVE

748
00:39:41,412 --> 00:39:45,644
AND THEN THEY'RE TOTALLY CONSUMED
AND ETERNALLY PERISH.

749
00:39:45,716 --> 00:39:47,980
''AND DO NOT FEAR THOSE
WHO KILL THE BODY

750
00:39:48,052 --> 00:39:49,986
''BUT CANNOT KILL THE SOUL,

751
00:39:50,054 --> 00:39:52,648
''BUT RATHER FEAR HIM
WHO IS ABLE TO DESTROY

752
00:39:52,723 --> 00:39:56,215
BOTH SOUL AND BODY IN HELL.''

753
00:39:56,293 --> 00:39:59,091
''FOR THE LIVING KNOW
THAT THEY WILL DIE,

754
00:39:59,163 --> 00:40:02,894
BUT THE DEAD KNOW NOTHING.''

755
00:40:03,367 --> 00:40:05,392
THE PRIESTS
BEGAN TO TEACH THAT HELL

756
00:40:05,469 --> 00:40:09,030
WAS A PLACE OF ETERNAL TORMENT
RULED BY THE DEVIL

757
00:40:09,106 --> 00:40:11,904
AND IT BEGAN
AT THE MOMENT OF DEATH.

758
00:40:11,976 --> 00:40:13,807
THE FALLEN CHURCH
WAS ABLE TO USE

759
00:40:13,878 --> 00:40:16,972
THIS FRIGHTFUL CONCEPT
OF NEVER-ENDING TORTURE

760
00:40:17,047 --> 00:40:21,279
TO TERRORIZE AND MANIPULATE
BOTH THE KING AND THE COMMONER.

761
00:40:21,352 --> 00:40:24,185
MOST TRAGIC OF ALL,
THIS FALSE TEACHING

762
00:40:24,255 --> 00:40:29,352
PORTRAYS JESUS AS SOME SORT
OF SADISTIC FIEND.

763
00:40:29,427 --> 00:40:32,191
IT'S ENCOURAGED
SOME ATHEISTS AND AGNOSTICS

764
00:40:32,263 --> 00:40:34,060
TO CHALLENGE CHRISTIANITY

765
00:40:34,131 --> 00:40:36,463
AND CHRISTIANITY'S IDEA
OF A LOVING GOD

766
00:40:36,734 --> 00:40:37,996
IF HE DOES SOMETHING

767
00:40:38,068 --> 00:40:41,003
THAT IS WORSE
THAN EVEN WHAT HITLER DID.

768
00:40:41,071 --> 00:40:43,301
NO MATTER
WHAT SOMEBODY HAS DONE,

769
00:40:43,374 --> 00:40:45,706
IS BILLIONS
OF YEARS OF TORTURE,

770
00:40:45,776 --> 00:40:47,903
FITTING THE CRIME?

771
00:40:47,978 --> 00:40:50,208
SO THERE HAVE BEEN PEOPLE
WHO HAVE HATED GOD

772
00:40:50,281 --> 00:40:55,014
AND HAVE LEARNED TO HATE GOD
BECAUSE OF THIS.

773
00:40:55,085 --> 00:40:58,851
ANOTHER PAGAN CONCEPT
THAT INFILTRATED CHRISTIAN THINKING

774
00:40:58,923 --> 00:41:01,221
WAS REGARDING THE AFTERLIFE.

775
00:41:01,292 --> 00:41:05,194
PURGATORY IS THE IDEA
THAT TEACHES THAT AT DEATH

776
00:41:05,262 --> 00:41:08,254
SOME PEOPLE WILL ENTER
A TEMPORARY HELLFIRE

777
00:41:08,332 --> 00:41:11,096
WHERE THEY'RE PURIFIED
FOR HEAVEN.

778
00:41:11,168 --> 00:41:13,363
PURGATORY'S A HALFWAY HOUSE,

779
00:41:13,437 --> 00:41:16,304
HALFWAY, KIND OF,
BETWEEN HEAVEN AND HELL.

780
00:41:16,373 --> 00:41:19,274
AND THE THING WITH PURGATORY
IS YOU CAN ESCAPE FROM IT.

781
00:41:19,343 --> 00:41:22,972
AS THE MASS SAYS,
''CONSIGNED TO FLAMES OF WOE,''

782
00:41:23,047 --> 00:41:27,507
IT'S FILLED WITH VERMIN,
IT'S FILLED WITH SULPHURIC SMELLS,

783
00:41:27,785 --> 00:41:30,276
IT MAY BE QUITE A BIT
BETTER THAN HELL,

784
00:41:30,354 --> 00:41:33,289
BUT IT'S NO PICNIC EITHER.

785
00:41:33,357 --> 00:41:35,825
THE CHURCH DEVELOPS GRADUALLY

786
00:41:35,893 --> 00:41:39,795
AND, AGAIN, IT GROWS
ON THE CHURCH BY SLOW DEGREES,

787
00:41:39,864 --> 00:41:43,459
THE IDEA
THAT ANYONE WHO DIES

788
00:41:43,534 --> 00:41:49,370
WITH THEIR WORKS
OF SATISFACTION INCOMPLETE

789
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:51,431
WILL PROBABLY
HAVE TO PAY THEM OFF

790
00:41:51,509 --> 00:41:55,775
IN SOME PLACE
OF POST-MORTEM SUFFERING.

791
00:41:55,846 --> 00:41:59,247
THEY ARE SUFFERING
IN ORDER TO BE PURIFIED,

792
00:41:59,316 --> 00:42:02,911
PURGED FROM THEIR SINS
AND OFFENSES

793
00:42:02,987 --> 00:42:05,148
WHICH THEY'VE COMMITTED IN LIFE.

794
00:42:05,222 --> 00:42:07,190
MEDIEVAL PEOPLE BELIEVED

795
00:42:07,258 --> 00:42:11,285
ALMOST EVERYONE
WILL BE SAVED AND REDEEMED,

796
00:42:11,362 --> 00:42:15,230
WHO IS A BAPTIZED
MEMBER OF THE CHURCH.

797
00:42:15,299 --> 00:42:21,499
BUT ALMOST EVERYONE WILL ALSO
HAVE TO MAKE SATISFACTION

798
00:42:21,572 --> 00:42:24,405
FOR THE SINS
THAT THEY'VE COMMITTED

799
00:42:24,475 --> 00:42:26,807
AND THAT THEY
HAVEN'T CONFESSED

800
00:42:26,877 --> 00:42:30,074
BY SPENDING SOME
TIME IN PURGATORY.

801
00:42:30,147 --> 00:42:33,412
SO THE REAL TASK THEN

802
00:42:33,484 --> 00:42:36,419
IS TO REDUCE
THE TIME IN PURGATORY.

803
00:42:36,487 --> 00:42:38,318
MANY PEOPLE MISUNDERSTAND
PURGATORY AND HELL.

804
00:42:38,389 --> 00:42:41,119
THERE'S AN IDEA YOU CAN
GET OUT OF HELL; YOU CAN'T.

805
00:42:41,191 --> 00:42:43,523
IF YOU GO TO HELL THAT'S IT.
THERE'S NO RELEASE.

806
00:42:43,594 --> 00:42:46,062
YOU'RE VERY, VERY WICKED
AND YOU'RE JUST DOOMED.

807
00:42:46,130 --> 00:42:48,189
BUT MOST PEOPLE,

808
00:42:48,265 --> 00:42:50,358
WE HAVE A LOT
OF BAD THINGS IN US

809
00:42:50,434 --> 00:42:52,561
SO HOW CAN WE
BE MADE GOOD FOR HEAVEN?

810
00:42:52,636 --> 00:42:55,002
WE HAVE TO HAVE IT
PURGED OUT OF US

811
00:42:55,072 --> 00:42:56,937
AND THUS
YOU GET THE WORD 'PURGATORY'.

812
00:42:57,007 --> 00:42:59,202
THEREFORE,
MOST CHRISTIANS BELIEVE

813
00:42:59,276 --> 00:43:02,143
THAT THEIR RELATIVES
ARE SUFFERING IN PURGATORY

814
00:43:02,212 --> 00:43:04,112
AND PURGATORY
IS NOT A NICE PLACE.

815
00:43:04,181 --> 00:43:07,446
YOU'RE THERE
FOR THOUSANDS OF YEARS.

816
00:43:07,518 --> 00:43:09,213
THE IDEA OF PURGATORY

817
00:43:09,286 --> 00:43:12,050
DATES BACK
CENTURIES BEFORE JESUS' TIME.

818
00:43:12,122 --> 00:43:15,216
WRITINGS FROM PLATO,
AS EARLY AS <i>4</i>00 BC,

819
00:43:15,292 --> 00:43:17,487
HELP SHED LIGHT
ON WHERE THIS CONCEPT

820
00:43:17,561 --> 00:43:20,462
OF PURIFICATION
AND PUNISHMENT CAME FROM.

821
00:43:20,531 --> 00:43:22,897
HOWEVER, PURGATORY
DIDN'T BECOME REGARDED

822
00:43:22,967 --> 00:43:26,494
AS AN ACTUAL PLACE
UNTIL CENTURIES LATER.

823
00:43:26,570 --> 00:43:29,903
BETWEEN 1 1 60 AND 1 1<i>8</i>0 AD,

824
00:43:29,974 --> 00:43:32,568
THEOLOGIANS DEVELOPED
THE DOCTRINE OF PURGATORY

825
00:43:32,643 --> 00:43:35,134
LEADING TO THE FORMAL
ACCEPTANCE OF IT

826
00:43:35,212 --> 00:43:39,444
AT THE SECOND COUNCIL
OF LYONS IN 1 2<i>7 4</i>.

827
00:43:39,516 --> 00:43:46,319
THE CHURCH THEN OFFERS
TO SUPPORT THE DEAD IN PURGATORY

828
00:43:47,191 --> 00:43:50,649
BY ITS PRAYERS
AND BY ATTRIBUTING TO PEOPLE

829
00:43:50,928 --> 00:43:55,194
THE BENEFITS OF THE SACRAMENTS,
ESPECIALLY THE COMMUNION.

830
00:43:55,265 --> 00:43:57,062
THIS IS ALL PERFECTLY ORTHODOX.

831
00:43:57,134 --> 00:43:59,602
THE CHURCH BELIEVED
THAT THIS IS DOING GOOD

832
00:43:59,670 --> 00:44:01,365
AND LAYPEOPLE
SEEMED TO BE WILLING

833
00:44:01,438 --> 00:44:04,032
TO PUT LARGE AMOUNTS
OF MONEY INTO IT

834
00:44:04,108 --> 00:44:05,405
AND YOU HAVE

835
00:44:05,476 --> 00:44:09,003
AN EXTRAORDINARY
PROLIFERATION OF INSTITUTIONS

836
00:44:09,079 --> 00:44:12,139
FOUNDED PRINCIPALLY FOR PRIESTS

837
00:44:12,216 --> 00:44:14,912
TO SAY MASSES FOR THE SOULS
OF THE DEPARTED,

838
00:44:14,985 --> 00:44:17,613
PARTICULARLY
IN THE 1 <i>4</i>TH AND 1<i>5</i>TH CENTURIES.

839
00:44:17,688 --> 00:44:19,588
THIS DOCTRINE WAS FABRICATED

840
00:44:19,657 --> 00:44:23,024
TO MANIPULATE THE MASSES
FOR FINANCIAL GAIN.

841
00:44:23,093 --> 00:44:25,459
PEOPLE WERE WILLING TO PAY
HUGE AMOUNTS OF MONEY

842
00:44:25,529 --> 00:44:27,019
TO RELEASE A LOVED ONE

843
00:44:27,097 --> 00:44:28,621
FROM THE TORTURES
OF PURGATORY.

844
00:44:28,699 --> 00:44:31,065
OF COURSE, BELIEVERS
COULD NEVER REALLY BE SURE

845
00:44:31,135 --> 00:44:33,103
WHEN SOMEONE LEFT PURGATORY,

846
00:44:33,170 --> 00:44:34,501
SO THE MONEY KEPT FLOWING

847
00:44:34,571 --> 00:44:37,404
INTO THE POCKETS
OF CORRUPT PRIESTS.

848
00:44:37,474 --> 00:44:38,941
THE HEAD OF THE CHURCH

849
00:44:39,009 --> 00:44:41,443
WOULD HAVE PEOPLE
GOING OUT TO RAISE MONEY

850
00:44:41,512 --> 00:44:44,003
AND ENCOURAGE PEOPLE
TO GIVE THEIR MONEY TO THE CHURCH,

851
00:44:44,081 --> 00:44:45,343
BUY PEOPLE OUT OF PURGATORY,

852
00:44:45,416 --> 00:44:48,476
SO THEY COULD FUND
THESE ELABORATE BUILDINGS.

853
00:44:48,552 --> 00:44:50,247
THIS BELIEF IN PURGATORY

854
00:44:50,320 --> 00:44:52,686
IS ALSO BUILT
ON THE DANGEROUS CONCEPT

855
00:44:52,756 --> 00:44:55,190
THAT THE WORKS
AND THE PRAYERS OF THE LIVING

856
00:44:55,259 --> 00:44:59,127
CAN SOMEHOW ALTER
THE DESTINY OF THE DEAD,

857
00:44:59,196 --> 00:45:04,099
YET JESUS MADE IT VERY CLEAR
THERE IS NO LIMBO OR PURGATORY.

